          "date": "2016-07-25 22:03:56.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-8339 lnet: lock improvement for ko2iblnd",
        "message": "LU-8339 lnet: lock improvement for ko2iblnd\n\nkiblnd_check_sends() takes conn::ibc_lock at the beginning\nand releases this lock at the end. This is inefficient because\nmost use-cases need to explicitly release ibc_lock before caling\nthis function.\n\nThis patch changes it to kiblnd_check_sends_locked() and avoids\nunnecessary lock dances.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang.zhen@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Doug Oucharek <doug.s.oucharek@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie90baae36cc32c469e00dea7f5207fac2d8cc854\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
